Skirting
Confirm all Skirting is installed as per plans
*Skirting should be installed on every plasterboard wall*
Ensure all skirting intersection are neat
Ensure there are not visible joints in skirting

Ensure skirting rebate is cleanly installed
Ensure there's no bowing in the skirting
Confirm skirting is installed with correct gap for expanation joint (2-3mm)
*Only if expanition joint is required*
Attach contractor ITP
Record photos of skirting

Ensure there are no visible brush strokes
